{
  "stem": "717.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Also, at, in the fifth grade, it was not officially, but practically officially, automatic that we joined an organization, a children's organization, that was affiliated with the Bund, with the Yiddish Socialist Party, the labor party of, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The organization was called SKIF.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "These initials, S-K-I-F, Sotsyalistishe Kinder Farband, which is the Socialist Yiddish Children's Organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We went to camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We had groups, you know, like, seminars every week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One of the happiest moments of my life before the war-- I remember that it was shortly before the Second World War.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This was either July or August, 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my parents finally permitted me to go to a summer camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was a four-week camp about 60 or 70 miles from Lodz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember going by bus, and I was sick like a dog on the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The camp was in a little village called Zondlowice, which was about 12 kilometers from a town Spala where the Polish president had a summer residence.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In fact, we had an excursion there one day to go there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And this is very memorable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "These four weeks in that camp, something that I still remember, even though it's already, what, 55 years.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were the happiest moments in my life before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On that camp, it was called the Ninth Socialist Children's Republic in Zondlowice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think there were about 100 children, ages from 12, maybe even younger, 11, till about 15 or 16.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a wonderful time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were games every day and discussion groups and excursions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was one day that we worked in the fields where the peasants-- with the Polish peasants.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was in July or August one day.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
